developed by
  Michal Belica
  Marcel Hecko
who based this code on top of code from
  Ihsan Kehribar

This is a temperature reading application - reads temperature sensor information from ATTiny internal TEMP sensor or an additional digital 1-Wire temperature sensor and presents them to the user in varios forms.

It is a application which also automatically sends the data with temperature information to tmeperme.com cloud-based temperature monitoring platform.

So far this code is a proof-of-concept code.
